@startuml
title 风控集成流程 (Risk Control Integration Flow)

actor User as "买家"
participant OrderCore as "order-core"
participant RiskPreCheck as "RiskPreCheckInterceptor"
participant Redis as "Redis(黑白名单缓存)"
participant ExternalRisk as "外部风控平台"
participant ReviewQueue as "异步审核队列\n(RocketMQ)"
participant HOLD as "HOLD Manager"
participant Admin as "风控运营(人工审核)"

== 正常下单风控检查 PASS ==
User -> OrderCore: 提交订单
OrderCore -> RiskPreCheck: preCheck(order, user)

RiskPreCheck -> Redis: 检查黑名单 (user, device, ip)
Redis --> RiskPreCheck: 未命中

RiskPreCheck -> Redis: 检查白名单 (user)
Redis --> RiskPreCheck: 未命中

RiskPreCheck -> ExternalRisk: 风控评估 (order, user)
ExternalRisk --> RiskPreCheck: {decision: "PASS", score: 15}

RiskPreCheck --> OrderCore: {decision: "PASS"}
OrderCore -> OrderCore: 继续下单流程
OrderCore --> User: 下单成功

== 可疑订单 进入异步审核 ==
User -> OrderCore: 提交订单
OrderCore -> RiskPreCheck: preCheck(order, user)

RiskPreCheck -> Redis: 黑白名单检查 (均未命中)
RiskPreCheck -> ExternalRisk: 风控评估
ExternalRisk --> RiskPreCheck: {decision: "REVIEW", score: 55}

RiskPreCheck --> OrderCore: {decision: "REVIEW"}
OrderCore -> OrderCore: 下单成功 (标记为待审核)

RiskPreCheck -> ReviewQueue: 发送延迟消息 (10min)
Note right: topic: risk.review\ntag: AUTO_REVIEW\ndelay: 10min

== 10分钟后 自动重评估 ==
ReviewQueue -> RiskPreCheck: 消费 ReviewMessage
RiskPreCheck -> ExternalRisk: 重新风控查询 (order)
ExternalRisk --> RiskPreCheck: {decision: "REJECTED", score: 68}

RiskPreCheck -> HOLD: triggerHold(order, reason="RISK_CONTROL")
HOLD -> HOLD: 订单状态 → HOLD (复用ADR-039状态机)
HOLD -> OrderCore: risk.order_hold 事件
OrderCore -> OrderCore: 订单进入 HOLD 状态

== 人工审核 ==
Admin -> Admin: 查看 HOLD 队列
Admin -> HOLD: POST /v1/admin/risk/reviews/{id}/approve

alt 审核通过
    HOLD -> HOLD: HOLD → 原状态 (PENDING_PAY/PAID)
    HOLD -> OrderCore: risk.order_released 事件
    OrderCore -> OrderCore: 订单恢复正常流转
else 审核拒绝
    HOLD -> HOLD: HOLD → CANCELLED
    HOLD -> OrderCore: order.cancelled 事件 (触发Saga补偿)
end

== 退款风控评分 ==
User -> OrderCore: 提交退款请求
OrderCore -> RiskPreCheck: refundScore(order, user)
RiskPreCheck -> ExternalRisk: 退款风控评估
ExternalRisk --> RiskPreCheck: {score: 25}

alt score < 30 + 金额≤200 + 未发货
    RiskPreCheck --> OrderCore: AUTO_APPROVE
    OrderCore -> OrderCore: 自动审核通过, 发起退款
else 30 ≤ score < 70 或 金额>200
    RiskPreCheck --> OrderCore: MANUAL_REVIEW
    OrderCore -> OrderCore: 入退款审核工单
else score ≥ 70
    RiskPreCheck --> OrderCore: REJECT
    OrderCore -> OrderCore: 退款拒绝
end

@enduml
